&lt;p&gt;2019-12-11'da VirtualBox'un yeni s&amp;uuml;r&amp;uuml;m&amp;uuml; yay&amp;inodot;nland&amp;inodot;. Ancak bu g&amp;uuml;ncellemeyle birlikte Vagrant ile VirtualBox aras&amp;inodot;nda bir uyumsuzluk sorunu ortaya &amp;ccedil;&amp;inodot;kt&amp;inodot;. Vagrant'&amp;inodot; &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;t&amp;inodot;rd&amp;inodot;&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot;zda a&amp;scedil;a&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;daki hata mesaj&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; alabilirsiniz:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;The&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;provider&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s1"&gt;'virtualbox'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;that&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;was&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;requested&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;to&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;back&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;the&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;machine&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s1"&gt;'homestead'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;is&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;reporting&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;that&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;it&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;isn&lt;span class="err"&gt;'&lt;/span&gt;t&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;usable&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;on&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;this&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;system.
The&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;reason&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;is&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;shown&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;below:
Vagrant&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;has&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;detected&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;that&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;you&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;have&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;a&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;version&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;of&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;VirtualBox&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;installed&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;that&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;is&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;not&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;supported&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;by&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;this&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;version&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;of&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Vagrant.&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Please&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;install&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;one&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;of&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;the&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;supported&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;versions&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;listed&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;below&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;to&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;use&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Vagrant:
&lt;span class="m"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;.0,&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;.1,&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;.2,&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;.3,&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;.0,&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;.1,&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;.2,&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;.0
A&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Vagrant&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;update&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;may&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;also&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;be&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;available&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;that&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;adds&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;support&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;for&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;the&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;version&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;you&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;specified.&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Please&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;check&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;www.vagrantup.com/downloads.html&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;to&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;download&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;the&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;latest&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;version.
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;VirtualBox 6.0'dan sonraki s&amp;uuml;r&amp;uuml;mler i&amp;ccedil;in gerekli d&amp;uuml;zenlemeler hen&amp;uuml;z yap&amp;inodot;lmam&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;t&amp;inodot;. Ancak Oracle k&amp;inodot;sa s&amp;uuml;re i&amp;ccedil;inde bir makale yay&amp;inodot;nlayarak bu soruna &amp;ccedil;&amp;ouml;z&amp;uuml;m sundu. &amp;Idot;&amp;scedil;te ad&amp;inodot;m ad&amp;inodot;m yap&amp;inodot;lmas&amp;inodot; gerekenler:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="adim-1-metarb-dosyasini-duzenleyin"&gt;Ad&amp;inodot;m 1: meta.rb Dosyas&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; D&amp;uuml;zenleyin&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A&amp;scedil;a&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;daki yolu izleyerek &lt;code&gt;meta.rb&lt;/code&gt; dosyas&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; a&amp;ccedil;&amp;inodot;n:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Linux/Mac&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;code&gt;/opt/vagrant/embedded/gems/2.2.6/gems/vagrant-2.2.6/plugins/providers/virtualbox/driver/meta.rb&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Windows&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;code&gt;C:\HashiCorp\Vagrant\embedded\gems\2.2.6\gems\vagrant-2.2.6\plugins\providers\virtualbox\driver\meta.rb&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dosyaya a&amp;scedil;a&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;daki sat&amp;inodot;r&amp;inodot; ekleyin:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class="vi"&gt;@logger&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;debug&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"Finding driver for VirtualBox version: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="si"&gt;#{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="vc"&gt;@@version&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="si"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;driver_map&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="w"&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"4.0"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="no"&gt;Version_4_0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="w"&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"4.1"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="no"&gt;Version_4_1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="w"&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"4.2"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="no"&gt;Version_4_2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="w"&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"4.3"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="no"&gt;Version_4_3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="w"&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"5.0"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="no"&gt;Version_5_0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="w"&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"5.1"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="no"&gt;Version_5_1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="w"&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"5.2"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="no"&gt;Version_5_2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="w"&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"6.0"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="no"&gt;Version_6_0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="w"&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"6.1"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="no"&gt;Version_6_1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="p"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="info-box important"&gt;
&lt;b&gt;Not:&lt;/b&gt; Windows kullan&amp;inodot;c&amp;inodot;lar&amp;inodot; dosyay&amp;inodot; d&amp;uuml;zenlerken &lt;b&gt;Notepad++&lt;/b&gt; veya &lt;b&gt;Visual Studio Code&lt;/b&gt; gibi bir metin edit&amp;ouml;r&amp;uuml;n&amp;uuml; &lt;b&gt;y&amp;ouml;netici &lt;/b&gt;olarak &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;t&amp;inodot;rmal&amp;inodot;d&amp;inodot;r.
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2 id="adim-2-version_6_1rb-dosyasini-olusturun"&gt;Ad&amp;inodot;m 2: version_6_1.rb Dosyas&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; Olu&amp;scedil;turun&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ayn&amp;inodot; dizinde &lt;code&gt;version_6_1.rb&lt;/code&gt; ad&amp;inodot;nda bir dosya olu&amp;scedil;turun. E&amp;gbreve;er u&amp;gbreve;ra&amp;scedil;mak istemiyorsan&amp;inodot;z, haz&amp;inodot;r dosyay&amp;inodot; a&amp;scedil;a&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;daki ba&amp;gbreve;lant&amp;inodot;lardan indirebilirsiniz:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.coter.net/upload/version_6_1.rb" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;version_6_1.rb (Alternatif 1)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.mediafire.com/file/wzq4l2xe6ul2dnw/version_6_1.rb/file" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;version_6_1.rb (Alternatif 2)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="adim-3-pluginrb-dosyasina-gerekli-satiri-ekleyin"&gt;Ad&amp;inodot;m 3: plugin.rb Dosyas&amp;inodot;na Gerekli Sat&amp;inodot;r&amp;inodot; Ekleyin&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bir &amp;uuml;st dizine &amp;ccedil;&amp;inodot;k&amp;inodot;n ve &lt;code&gt;plugin.rb&lt;/code&gt; dosyas&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; a&amp;ccedil;&amp;inodot;n. A&amp;scedil;a&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;daki sat&amp;inodot;r&amp;inodot; ekleyin:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;module&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nn"&gt;Driver&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="w"&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;autoload&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ss"&gt;:Meta&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="no"&gt;File&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;expand_path&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"../driver/meta"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="bp"&gt;__FILE__&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
