&lt;span class="w"&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;autoload&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ss"&gt;:Version_5_0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="no"&gt;File&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;expand_path&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"../driver/version_5_0"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="bp"&gt;__FILE__&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="w"&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;autoload&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ss"&gt;:Version_5_1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="no"&gt;File&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;expand_path&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"../driver/version_5_1"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="bp"&gt;__FILE__&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="w"&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;autoload&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ss"&gt;:Version_5_2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="no"&gt;File&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;expand_path&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"../driver/version_5_2"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="bp"&gt;__FILE__&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="w"&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;autoload&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ss"&gt;:Version_6_0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="no"&gt;File&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;expand_path&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"../driver/version_6_0"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="bp"&gt;__FILE__&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="w"&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;autoload&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ss"&gt;:Version_6_1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="no"&gt;File&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;expand_path&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"../driver/version_6_1"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="bp"&gt;__FILE__&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="k"&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2 id="sonuc"&gt;Sonu&amp;ccedil;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yukar&amp;inodot;daki i&amp;scedil;lemleri tamamlad&amp;inodot;ktan sonra Vagrant'&amp;inodot; tekrar &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;t&amp;inodot;r&amp;inodot;n. Art&amp;inodot;k VirtualBox 6.1 ile uyumlu bir &amp;scedil;ekilde &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;mas&amp;inodot; gerekiyor. E&amp;gbreve;er hala hata al&amp;inodot;yorsan&amp;inodot;z, yorumlarda payla&amp;scedil;maktan &amp;ccedil;ekinmeyin! 👍💗&lt;/p&gt;</content><category term="program"></category><category term="linux"></category><category term="vagrant"></category><category term="windows10"></category></entry><entry><title>Windows Üzerinde Redshift Kullanımı</title><link href="https://yuceltoluyag.dev/windows-uzerinde-redshift-kullanimi/" rel="alternate"></link><published>2019-12-04T10:00:00+03:00</published><updated>2025-03-08T12:00:00+03:00</updated><author><name>yuceltoluyag</name></author><id>tag:yuceltoluyag.dev,2019-12-04:/windows-uzerinde-redshift-kullanimi/</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Windows işletim sisteminde Redshift programını nasıl kullanacağınızı adım adım anlatıyoruz. Göz sağlığınızı korumak için en iyi ayarları keşfedin! 👀&lt;/p&gt;</summary><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Redshift Windows" src="/images/redshift_windows.webp"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="redshift-nedir"&gt;🌙 Redshift Nedir?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Redshift, &amp;ouml;zellikle gece saatlerinde bilgisayar kullananlar i&amp;ccedil;in harika bir ara&amp;ccedil;t&amp;inodot;r. Program, g&amp;uuml;n do&amp;gbreve;umu ve g&amp;uuml;n bat&amp;inodot;m&amp;inodot;na g&amp;ouml;re ekran&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot;z&amp;inodot;n renk s&amp;inodot;cakl&amp;inodot;&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; ve gamma ayarlar&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; otomatik olarak de&amp;gbreve;i&amp;scedil;tirir. B&amp;ouml;ylece g&amp;ouml;z yorgunlu&amp;gbreve;unu azalt&amp;inodot;r ve daha konforlu bir deneyim sunar. 😌&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="alternatif-programlar"&gt;🚀 Alternatif Programlar&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Redshift kullanmadan &amp;ouml;nce birka&amp;ccedil; alternatif program denedim:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Windows Gece I&amp;scedil;&amp;inodot;&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot; (Night Mode)&lt;/strong&gt;: Windows'un yerle&amp;scedil;ik &amp;ouml;zelli&amp;gbreve;i olsa da esneklik a&amp;ccedil;&amp;inodot;s&amp;inodot;ndan yetersiz.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Flux&lt;/strong&gt;: &amp;Idot;lk s&amp;uuml;r&amp;uuml;mleri ba&amp;scedil;ar&amp;inodot;l&amp;inodot;yd&amp;inodot;, ancak zamanla baz&amp;inodot; eksiklikler ortaya &amp;ccedil;&amp;inodot;kt&amp;inodot;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Redshift&lt;/strong&gt;: Linux'ta uzun s&amp;uuml;redir sorunsuz kulland&amp;inodot;&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;m i&amp;ccedil;in Windows'ta da denemeye karar verdim. A&amp;ccedil;&amp;inodot;k kaynakl&amp;inodot; ve &amp;ccedil;apraz platform deste&amp;gbreve;i sayesinde Windows'ta da &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;t&amp;inodot;rmak m&amp;uuml;mk&amp;uuml;n. 💡&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="redshift-nasil-kurulur"&gt;🔧 Redshift Nas&amp;inodot;l Kurulur?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/jonls/redshift/releases" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;Redshift'in en son s&amp;uuml;r&amp;uuml;m&amp;uuml;n&amp;uuml;&lt;/a&gt; indirin.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;C:\Program Files (x86)&lt;/strong&gt; i&amp;ccedil;ine &lt;strong&gt;Redshift&lt;/strong&gt; ad&amp;inodot;nda bir klas&amp;ouml;r olu&amp;scedil;turun.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;Idot;ndirdi&amp;gbreve;iniz dosyalar&amp;inodot; bu klas&amp;ouml;r&amp;uuml;n i&amp;ccedil;ine &amp;ccedil;&amp;inodot;kar&amp;inodot;n.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gamma s&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot;rlar&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; kald&amp;inodot;rmak i&amp;ccedil;in gerekli kay&amp;inodot;t defteri (reg) dosyalar&amp;inodot;na ihtiyac&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot;z var. &lt;a href="http://www.mediafire.com/file/ylw89legwkyp04t/redshift.7z/file" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;Buradan&lt;/a&gt; indirebilirsiniz.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;📂 &lt;strong&gt;Klas&amp;ouml;r d&amp;uuml;zeni &amp;scedil;u &amp;scedil;ekilde olmal&amp;inodot;:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;C&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:\&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;Program&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Files&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;x86&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)\&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;Redshift&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;boxvr;&amp;boxh;&amp;boxh;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;redshift&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;exe&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;boxvr;&amp;boxh;&amp;boxh;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;redshift&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;conf&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;boxvr;&amp;boxh;&amp;boxh;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;di&amp;gbreve;er&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;dosyalar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;...&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2 id="redshift-ayarlari"&gt;⚙️ Redshift Ayarlar&amp;inodot;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Redshift'i ba&amp;scedil;latmadan &amp;ouml;nce baz&amp;inodot; yap&amp;inodot;land&amp;inodot;rmalar yapman&amp;inodot;z gerekiyor:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Windows + R&lt;/strong&gt; tu&amp;scedil;lar&amp;inodot;na basarak &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;t&amp;inodot;r penceresini a&amp;ccedil;&amp;inodot;n.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;*&lt;em&gt;%USERPROFILE%\AppData\Local*&lt;/em&gt; dizinine gidin.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;redshift.conf&lt;/strong&gt; ad&amp;inodot;nda yeni bir dosya olu&amp;scedil;turun.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.latlong.net/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;LatLong.net&lt;/a&gt; sitesine giderek bulundu&amp;gbreve;unuz konumun enlem (latitude) ve boylam (longitude) bilgilerini al&amp;inodot;n.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;redshift.conf&lt;/strong&gt; dosyan&amp;inodot;z&amp;inodot; a&amp;scedil;a&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;daki gibi d&amp;uuml;zenleyin:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;[redshift]
; G&amp;uuml;n ve gece ekran s&amp;inodot;cakl&amp;inodot;klar&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; belirleyin
temp-day=6500
temp-night=5500
transition=1
brightness-day=1
brightness-night=0.7
gamma-day=0.8:0.7:0.8
gamma-night=0.8
location-provider=manual
adjustment-method=wingdi

[manual]
lat=xx
lon=yy
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;📌 &lt;strong&gt;Not:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;code&gt;lat=xx&lt;/code&gt; ve &lt;code&gt;lon=yy&lt;/code&gt; k&amp;inodot;s&amp;inodot;mlar&amp;inodot;na kendi konum bilgilerinizi eklemeyi unutmay&amp;inodot;n!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="redshifti-baslatma"&gt;▶️ Redshift'i Ba&amp;scedil;latma&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Redshift.exe&lt;/strong&gt; dosyas&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;t&amp;inodot;r&amp;inodot;n.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ekran renk s&amp;inodot;cakl&amp;inodot;&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot;n yava&amp;scedil;&amp;ccedil;a de&amp;gbreve;i&amp;scedil;ti&amp;gbreve;ini g&amp;ouml;zlemleyin.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;E&amp;gbreve;er herhangi bir hata al&amp;inodot;rsan&amp;inodot;z, &lt;strong&gt;redshift.conf&lt;/strong&gt; dosyan&amp;inodot;z&amp;inodot;n do&amp;gbreve;ru yap&amp;inodot;land&amp;inodot;r&amp;inodot;ld&amp;inodot;&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; kontrol edin.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;hr/&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Redshift, ekran&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot;z&amp;inodot; g&amp;ouml;z dostu hale getirerek gece &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;malar&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot;z&amp;inodot; daha konforlu hale getirecektir. 🌟 &amp;Ouml;zellikle programc&amp;inodot;lar, yazarlar ve uzun s&amp;uuml;re bilgisayar ba&amp;scedil;&amp;inodot;nda vakit ge&amp;ccedil;iren herkes i&amp;ccedil;in olduk&amp;ccedil;a faydal&amp;inodot;d&amp;inodot;r. 🖥️💙&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sorular&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot;z&amp;inodot; veya deneyimlerinizi yorumlarda payla&amp;scedil;abilirsiniz! 🎤&lt;/p&gt;</content><category term="program"></category><category term="windows10"></category><category term="redshift"></category><category term="gece_modu"></category></entry><entry><title>VLSub ile Altyazı Aramaya Son (Resimli Anlatım)</title><link href="https://yuceltoluyag.dev/vlsub-ile-altyazi-aramaya-son/" rel="alternate"></link><published>2019-03-30T10:00:00+03:00</published><updated>2025-03-08T12:00:00+03:00</updated><author><name>yuceltoluyag</name></author><id>tag:yuceltoluyag.dev,2019-03-30:/vlsub-ile-altyazi-aramaya-son/</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;VLC medya oynatıcısı için VLSub eklentisiyle kolayca altyazı bulma ve indirme yöntemlerini anlatıyoruz.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><content type="html">&lt;h1 id="vlsub-ile-altyazi-aramaya-son-resimli-anlatim"&gt;VLSub ile Altyaz&amp;inodot; Aramaya Son (Resimli Anlat&amp;inodot;m) 🎬&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Merhaba! Y&amp;inodot;llard&amp;inodot;r severek kulland&amp;inodot;&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;m ve her film ya da dizi izledi&amp;gbreve;imde mutlaka &amp;ouml;nerdi&amp;gbreve;im &lt;strong&gt;VLSub&lt;/strong&gt; eklentisinden bahsedece&amp;gbreve;im. Film ve dizileri &lt;strong&gt;orijinal sesleriyle, altyaz&amp;inodot;l&amp;inodot;&lt;/strong&gt; izlemeyi seviyorum &amp;ccedil;&amp;uuml;nk&amp;uuml; bu, hem dile a&amp;scedil;inal&amp;inodot;k kazand&amp;inodot;r&amp;inodot;yor hem de yap&amp;inodot;m&amp;inodot; daha do&amp;gbreve;al bir &amp;scedil;ekilde deneyimlememi sa&amp;gbreve;l&amp;inodot;yor. Eskiden altyaz&amp;inodot;lar&amp;inodot; manuel olarak bulup uyumlu olup olmad&amp;inodot;&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; test etmek zorundayd&amp;inodot;k. Neyse ki &lt;strong&gt;VLSub&lt;/strong&gt;, bu s&amp;uuml;reci otomatikle&amp;scedil;tirerek bize b&amp;uuml;y&amp;uuml;k bir kolayl&amp;inodot;k sa&amp;gbreve;l&amp;inodot;yor! 🚀&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr/&gt;
&lt;div class="info-box tip"&gt;
&lt;b&gt;Bilgi:&lt;/b&gt; Yeni VLC s&amp;uuml;r&amp;uuml;mlerinde bu &amp;ouml;zellik &lt;b&gt;yerle&amp;scedil;ik olarak&lt;/b&gt; gelebilir. E&amp;gbreve;er &lt;b&gt;G&amp;ouml;r&amp;uuml;n&amp;uuml;m&lt;/b&gt; sekmesinde &lt;b&gt;VLSub&lt;/b&gt; men&amp;uuml;s&amp;uuml;n&amp;uuml; g&amp;ouml;r&amp;uuml;yorsan&amp;inodot;z, ayr&amp;inodot;ca bir eklenti kurman&amp;inodot;za gerek yoktur. ✅
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;hr/&gt;
&lt;h2 id="kurulum"&gt;🛠 Kurulum&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.videolan.org/vlc/index.tr.html" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;VLC Media Player&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; program&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; indirin ve kurun. (Tamamen &amp;uuml;cretsiz ve a&amp;ccedil;&amp;inodot;k kaynak kodludur.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;E&amp;gbreve;er &lt;strong&gt;G&amp;ouml;r&amp;uuml;n&amp;uuml;m&lt;/strong&gt; men&amp;uuml;s&amp;uuml; alt&amp;inodot;nda &lt;strong&gt;VLSub&lt;/strong&gt; se&amp;ccedil;ene&amp;gbreve;ini g&amp;ouml;remiyorsan&amp;inodot;z, &amp;scedil;u ad&amp;inodot;mlar&amp;inodot; izleyin:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="VLSub Kurulumu" src="/images/vlsub0.webp"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://addons.videolan.org/p/1154045/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;Buradan&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; eklentiyi indirin.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;C:\Program Files\VideoLAN\VLC\lua\extensions&lt;/strong&gt; dizinine kopyalay&amp;inodot;n.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;VLC kapal&amp;inodot; olmal&amp;inodot;d&amp;inodot;r!&lt;/strong&gt; Kopyalama i&amp;scedil;lemini yapt&amp;inodot;ktan sonra VLC'yi yeniden ba&amp;scedil;lat&amp;inodot;n.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr/&gt;
&lt;h2 id="eklenti-dizinleri-farkli-isletim-sistemleri-icin"&gt;📂 Eklenti Dizinleri (Farkl&amp;inodot; &amp;Idot;&amp;scedil;letim Sistemleri &amp;Idot;&amp;ccedil;in)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Windows (T&amp;uuml;m Kullan&amp;inodot;c&amp;inodot;lar):&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;code&gt;%ProgramFiles%\VideoLAN\VLC\lua\extensions&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Windows (Ge&amp;ccedil;erli Kullan&amp;inodot;c&amp;inodot;):&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;code&gt;%APPDATA%\vlc\lua\extensions&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Linux (T&amp;uuml;m Kullan&amp;inodot;c&amp;inodot;lar):&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;code&gt;/usr/lib/vlc/lua/extensions/&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Linux (Ge&amp;ccedil;erli Kullan&amp;inodot;c&amp;inodot;):&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;code&gt;~/.local/share/vlc/lua/extensions/&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mac OS X (T&amp;uuml;m Kullan&amp;inodot;c&amp;inodot;lar):&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;code&gt;/Applications/VLC.app/Contents/MacOS/share/lua/extensions/&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mac OS X (Ge&amp;ccedil;erli Kullan&amp;inodot;c&amp;inodot;):&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;code&gt;/Users/%your_name%/Library/Application Support/org.videolan.vlc/lua/extensions/&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr/&gt;
&lt;h2 id="altyazi-bulma"&gt;🔍 Altyaz&amp;inodot; Bulma&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;Idot;zleyece&amp;gbreve;iniz videoyu a&amp;ccedil;&amp;inodot;n.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Men&amp;uuml;den&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;code&gt;G&amp;ouml;r&amp;uuml;n&amp;uuml;m -&amp;gt; VLSub&lt;/code&gt; se&amp;ccedil;ene&amp;gbreve;ine t&amp;inodot;klay&amp;inodot;n.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="VLSub A&amp;ccedil;ma" src="/images/vlbsub.webp"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A&amp;ccedil;&amp;inodot;lan pencerede film ya da dizi ismini otomatik arayabilir veya manuel olarak girebilirsiniz.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sonu&amp;ccedil;lardan birine t&amp;inodot;klay&amp;inodot;n&lt;/strong&gt; ve &lt;strong&gt;Download Selection&lt;/strong&gt; butonuna bas&amp;inodot;n.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Altyaz&amp;inodot; &lt;strong&gt;otomatik olarak ayn&amp;inodot; klas&amp;ouml;re&lt;/strong&gt; indirilecektir.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="VLSub Altyaz&amp;inodot; Bulma" src="/images/vlsub1.webp"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr/&gt;
&lt;h2 id="i-ekstra-bilgi"&gt;ℹ️ Ekstra Bilgi&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Baz&amp;inodot; video dosyalar&amp;inodot;nda &lt;strong&gt;"altyaz&amp;inodot; var"&lt;/strong&gt; ibaresi olsa da, i&amp;ccedil;indeki altyaz&amp;inodot;lar &amp;Idot;ngilizce ya da farkl&amp;inodot; bir dilde olabilir. &amp;Ouml;zellikle b&amp;uuml;y&amp;uuml;k dosyalarda bu durum s&amp;inodot;k g&amp;ouml;r&amp;uuml;l&amp;uuml;r. VLSub sayesinde, &lt;strong&gt;t&amp;uuml;m sezonlar&amp;inodot; veya tek bir b&amp;ouml;l&amp;uuml;m&amp;uuml; kolayca tarayarak&lt;/strong&gt; do&amp;gbreve;ru altyaz&amp;inodot;y&amp;inodot; bulabilirsiniz. 😎&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Altyaz&amp;inodot; arama zahmetinden kurtulun ve keyifle izlemeye devam edin! 🎥🍿&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sorular&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot;z veya &amp;ouml;nerileriniz varsa yorumlarda belirtmeyi unutmay&amp;inodot;n!&lt;/strong&gt; 🤗&lt;/p&gt;</content><category term="program"></category><category term="vlc"></category><category term="film"></category></entry><entry><title>Spotify’dan Müzik Nasıl İndirilir? (Resimli Anlatım - Güncel)</title><link href="https://yuceltoluyag.dev/spotify-muzik-indirme/" rel="alternate"></link><published>2018-09-10T10:00:00+03:00</published><updated>2025-03-08T12:00:00+03:00</updated><author><name>yuceltoluyag</name></author><id>tag:yuceltoluyag.dev,2018-09-10:/spotify-muzik-indirme/</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Spotify’dan müzik indirme yöntemlerini resimli ve güncel anlatımla keşfedin.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><content type="html">&lt;h1 id="neden"&gt;Neden?&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Merhaba! &lt;strong&gt;Spotify&lt;/strong&gt;, &amp;ccedil;evrimd&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;&amp;inodot; m&amp;uuml;zik dinleme &amp;ouml;zelli&amp;gbreve;ini yaln&amp;inodot;zca &lt;strong&gt;premium&lt;/strong&gt; abonelerine sunuyor. Ancak, bu anlat&amp;inodot;mda premium hesap kullanmadan be&amp;gbreve;endi&amp;gbreve;iniz &amp;ccedil;alma listelerini nas&amp;inodot;l &amp;uuml;cretsiz olarak indirebilece&amp;gbreve;inizi ad&amp;inodot;m ad&amp;inodot;m g&amp;ouml;sterece&amp;gbreve;im.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;Idot;nternette &amp;ccedil;e&amp;scedil;itli &lt;strong&gt;Spotify downloader&lt;/strong&gt; ara&amp;ccedil;lar&amp;inodot; mevcut, ancak bunlar&amp;inodot;n &amp;ccedil;o&amp;gbreve;u ya d&amp;uuml;zg&amp;uuml;n &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;m&amp;inodot;yor ya da s&amp;uuml;reklilik sa&amp;gbreve;layam&amp;inodot;yor. Anlataca&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;m y&amp;ouml;ntem ise aylard&amp;inodot;r sorunsuz bir &amp;scedil;ekilde &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;&amp;inodot;yor ve olduk&amp;ccedil;a pratik!&lt;/p&gt;
