   &lt;a href="http://www.playlist-converter.net/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;Playlist Converter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Spotify sekmesine t&amp;inodot;klay&amp;inodot;n&lt;/strong&gt; ve ard&amp;inodot;ndan &lt;strong&gt;&amp;ldquo;Login with Spotify&amp;rdquo;&lt;/strong&gt; butonuna basarak hesab&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot;za giri&amp;scedil; yap&amp;inodot;n.&lt;/li&gt;
